  "texts": [
    "FMs can improve FL's efficiency in several ways.",
    "Starting Point Advantage: FMs provide a robust starting point for FL.",
    "Clients can begin fine-tuning directly on their local data instead of starting from scratch, leading to faster convergence and enhanced performance while reducing the need for extensive communication rounds [84,85].",
    "Data Diversity Enhancement: FMs act as powerful generators that can synthesize diverse data, enriching the training dataset in FL.",
    "An example is GPT-FL [86], which utilizes generative models to produce synthetic data that improves downstream model training on servers."
  ],
